text: Annecy-le-Vieux is a former commune. It is in Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes in the Haute-Savoie department in southeast France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the commune of Annecy.Arrêté préfectoral 14 July 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Haute-Savoie Category:Annecy
title: Annecy-le-Vieux
